{"tid":1589014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係咪已經忘記咗呢件事","createTime":"2019-09-23T05:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T05:39:06.000Z","uid":308028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ffed6c333589670debe62b40b43e9e920f12e5ca","tid":1589014,"uid":308028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌第一次開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n呢件事好想大家積極做返，就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十點鳩叫</span></span><br />\n我明白好多人已經攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過正正係活動係比自己<span style=\"color: gold;\">放鬆吓</span>，等自己可以抒發出黎！而且呢個活動可以<span style=\"color: gold;\">大大提升同激勵我哋嘅士氣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當你覺得自己孤單同頂唔順嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不妨等到十點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你就會知道各位手足都喺自己身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有一班人去癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰一刻真係好warm同更有動力行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以十點鳩叫真係好重要㗎！唔好俾佢停</span></span><br />\n同埋可以展示到我哋有幾咁團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且好有渲染力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />身邊有啲中立朋友正正因為咁而被感染變成淺黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以大家唔好睇小佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續十點窗邊鳩叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要聽到大家嘅叫聲啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXPf6ji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXPf6ji.jpg&h=dcf1c64c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66povLZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66povLZ.jpg&h=414780e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"cfb56e07d388167e0afe7e0ec6ac6001504b104c","tid":1589014,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"83655019a3b44294d67d76fa98df857e89b391e9","tid":1589014,"uid":55824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:39:06.000Z","msg":"推"}]}